title: TuneIn Radio Pro 7.3.Full
description:
Requirements: Android 1.6+

Overview: Browse and listen to radio -- live, local and global.

Listen to the world.

TuneIn is a new way to listen to the world through live local and global radio from 

wherever you are. Whether you want music, sports, news or current events, TuneIn 

offers over 50,000 stations and 1.2 million on-demand programs for you to choose 

from. The TuneIn Radio Pro app for Android puts this entire experience in the palm 

of your hand with the added benefit of recording what youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re listening to (requires 

memory card).

Important Update: This new version of TuneIn (5.3) includes Car Mode, which lets 

you listen to your favorite music, sports and news simply by speaking a command 

into your Android phone or tablet. This update also includes extra large buttons 

for easy viewing and control.

What's in this version:

* We've made TuneIn quicker, with the Now Playing screen and TuneIn Live tiles 

loading faster

* Sharing stations and live events through Google+ and Facebook is now easier than

* TuneIn works smoother between different Android devices, so whether you're using 

a phone or tablet, you'll have the best experience for that device

* We've fixed Twitter sharing so you can let your friends know when you've found a
